h2. Problem

I need an option to change the default playback rate. [Titanium.Media.AudioPlayer|http://developer.appcelerator.com/apidoc/mobile/latest/Titanium.Media.AudioPlayer-object] does not have a {{setPlaybackRate}} property.

This request is for all platforms - mobile and mobile web


h2. Use case

{code:lang=javascript|title=app.js}
var oAudio = Ti.Media.createAudioPlayer();
oAudio.src = "URL_OF_AUDIO.mp3";
oAudio.playbackRate = 2.0;
oAudio.play();
{code}

h2. Logs

n/a. The audio stil plays at original speed instead of double speed.

h2. Discussions

http://developer.appcelerator.com/question/128001/speedup-and-slowdown-audio-playback
